|---------|-------------------|----------|
| **production** | All secrets | Live environment |
| **deploy-preview** | High+ sensitivity | PR testing |
| **branch-deploy** | Medium+ sensitivity | Feature testing |

### Migration from .env

Use the migration script to move from local `.env` files:

```bash
