# Component Patterns

# Naming Conventions
- PascalCase for components: `UserProfile`, `CallTracker`
- camelCase for props: `isLoading`, `onCallEnd`
- kebab-case for CSS classes: `call-status`, `user-card`

# File Structure
```
ComponentName/
